{"tid":1825243,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"查三告兩 辯方：警針對年輕人","createTime":"2020-01-15T06:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T16:52:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e11b9efb5dd25992206fc043cf1b620a0dad6451","tid":1825243,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T06:07:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200115/354QZMCUSXCMSLQO6GXR7RVXZA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200115%2F354QZMCUSXCMSLQO6GXR7RVXZA%2F&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBi1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=81969c99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200115%2F354QZMCUSXCMSLQO6GXR7RVXZA%2F&h=89abf97d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200115/354QZMCUSXCMSLQO6GXR7RVXZA/</a><br />\n<br />\n查三告兩 辯方：警針對年輕人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200115/large/1579018521_b254.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200115%2Flarge%2F1579018521_b254.jpg&h=29479548&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告郭曉楠（左）及何志程（右）遭票控違反《公眾生及市政條例》。<br />\n<br />\n【貼文宣遭票控】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一對年輕男女8.5全港三罷當日，疑在青衣張貼反送中及三罷文宣，遭票控違反《公眾衞生及市政條例》，案件昨續審。辯方律師林志釉陳詞指，警員當時共截查三人，最終卻只控告兩名被告，「好明顯係針對年輕人」；並指警員作供時亦承認截查兩名被告期間程序有多處遺漏，例如搜身後沒有摘錄事件等。裁判官劉淑嫻將案件押後至下月27日裁決。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警認無目睹完整過程<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：撐警藍店成黃絲打卡熱點<br />\n<br />\n被告何志程（24歲）及郭曉楠（24歲）被指去年8月5日下午在青衣青荃路欄杆張貼三張海報，屬未經當局許可而在政府土地上張貼海報。<br />\n<br />\n姓葉途人昨供稱，當時聽見警員向男被告表示：「𠵱家懷疑你藏有違規物品，要搜袋。」事後警員又向男被告索取身份證稱：「純粹做個record啫。」<br />\n<br />\n辯方律師林志釉陳詞時指，警員作供時承認截查被告時有五項遺漏，包括忘記將女被告身上的膠紙帶回警署、三次忘記在使用警權後摘錄於記事冊，及忘記檢取七張海報後讓男被告簽署文件，警員當時向兩人索取個人資料時，也沒有說明事後或會將之作檢控用途。此外，警員承認沒親眼目睹二人貼海報的完整過程。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKS13795-6/19<br />\n■記者廖希呈"},{"pid":"ff153615fa7d333135d8d0d213d344f42adc5728","tid":1825243,"uid":271516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T06:09:04.000Z","msg":"純粹濫捕"},{"pid":"6c548d8f944a518124312196969237cf8efe6e0f","tid":1825243,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T06:13:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">沙田醫院:醫護界街站</span><br />\n時間 ： 1300-1500<br />\n地點 ：沙田醫院<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">灣仔:會計工會街站</span><br />\n時間 ： 1930-2130<br />\n地點 ：灣仔皇后大道東147-149號威利商業大廈22室灣仔Livo<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">荃灣公民廣場-法律權益及濫捕應對</span><br />\n時間 ： 2000-2200<br />\n地點 ：荃灣廣場對出空地<br />\n<br />\n===================================<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">中環:119天下制裁大遊行</span><br />\n日期：2020年1月19日 星期日<br />\n時間 ： 1500<br />\n地點 ：遮打道 至 銅鑼灣SOGO<br />\n(*不反對通知書申請中)"},{"pid":"35331768d6e7a64ef70f1b25acb2b2a248a9cd79","tid":1825243,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T06:24:58.000Z","msg":"乜都漏都有得告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86211324e6e388901a16cccee0608d987de92caf","tid":1825243,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:52:42.000Z","msg":"( please forward to your English reading friends, colleagues, etc) <br />\n<br />\nMan arrested after taking picture of Hong Kong police in restaurant, with councillor decrying incident as &lsquo;arbitrary arrest&rsquo; | South China Morning Post<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/law-and-crime/article/3046100/man-arrested-after-catching-hong-kong-police-camera\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Flaw-and-crime%2Farticle%2F3046100%2Fman-arrested-after-catching-hong-kong-police-camera&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBi1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=ddd66aa4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/law-and-crime/article/3046100/man-arrested-after-catching-hong-kong-police-camera</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/65L3WEf.j